<div class="home-container">
  <div class="sherpa_home_banner">
    <div class="sherpa_home_banner_head">
      <div class="sherpa_logo_banner">
        <%= cl_image_tag("Vector_Sherpa_uznxgg", width: 120, height: 150, crop: :fill) %>
      </div>
      <div class="sherpa_home_navbar">
        <ul class="home_navbar_buttons">
          <a href="#"><li><span class="highlight-blue">Teachers</span></li></a>
          <a href="#Students"><li><span class="highlight-blue">Students</span></li></a>
          <a href="#"><li><span class="highlight-blue">Product</span></li></a>
          <a href="#"><li><span class="highlight-blue">Customers</span></li></a>
          <a class="nav-link home-navbar-login" href="/users/sign_in">
            <li>Log in</li>
          </a>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="home-banner-text">
      <h1>Bring all students atop the learning curve</h1>
      <p>Get your institution onboarded on Sherpa today and offer your students a revolutionarily personalized learning experience. Interact with your different classes and improve your lessons thanks to our AI-powered suggestions.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="home-content-teachers" href="#teachers">
      <div class="home-content-card card-shadow-left">
        <h5><span class="highlight-orange">Your new digital assistant</span></h5>
        <p>Spend more time focusing on your lessons, less on analysing each student’s understanding. Sherpa helps you bring all your classes to unreachable summits.</p>
        <%= cl_image_tag("tv_aaagm4", width: 100, height: 100, crop: :fill) %>
      </div>
      <div class="home-content-card card-shadow-right">
        <h5><span class="highlight-orange">Everything to know about your classes at a glance</span></h5>
        <p>Sherpa helps you easily understand your classes’ behaviour and reactions to your lessons to adapt to their specificities.</p>
        <%= cl_image_tag("clipboard_azpfeg", width: 100, height: 100, crop: :fill) %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="home-content-students" href="#students">
      <div class="home-content-card card-shadow-left">
        <h5><span class="highlight-orange">Engage with all your students</span></h5>
        <p>Thanks to your Sherpa Forum, discuss chapters of your lessons with your students, answer all secret questions and encourage pair teaching.</p>
        <%= cl_image_tag("chat_mhpwh6", width: 100, height: 100, crop: :fill) %>
      </div>
      <div class="home-content-card card-shadow-right">
        <h5><span class="highlight-orange">Adapt to everyone’s pace</span></h5>
        <p>Adjust your lessons to your students’ difficulties and insure no one is left behind thanks to Sherpa’s AI powered suggestions.</p>
        <%= cl_image_tag("botanical_dudb1y", width: 100, height: 100, crop: :fill) %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="home-spacer"></div>
  <div class="product-features-container">
    <h1><span class="highlight-blue">Product</span></h1>
    <%= cl_image_tag("cube_zjcj6n", width: 100, height: 100, crop: :fill) %>
    <div class="gallery js-flickity"
      data-flickity-options='{ "wrapAround": true }'>
      <div class="gallery-cell"></div>
      <div class="gallery-cell"></div>
      <div class="gallery-cell"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="home-demo-booking">
    <div class="booking-flexbox">
      <%= cl_image_tag("calendar_zdi8oi", width: 200, height: 200, crop: :fill) %>
      <div class="book-demo-button"><button class="learn-more">BOOK A DEMO</button></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="customers-featuring-card">
    <%= cl_image_tag("hands_pnteee", width: 100, height: 100, crop: :fill) %>
    <h1><span class="highlight-blue">Our Customers</span></h1>
    <div class="customers-company-logos">
      <%= cl_image_tag("LeWagonvec_qjch18", width: 280, height: 87, crop: :fill) %>
      <%= cl_image_tag("edhec_vftwp4", width: 280, height: 80, crop: :fill) %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%= render 'shared/footer' %>
</div>
